	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 4: To do something without making any progress&lt;/strong&gt; (प्रगति के बिना कुछ करना): To engage in an activity without achieving any significant results.
