		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;Example: It was a compassionate speech, without being maudlin.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;Regalia&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; means official and traditional special clothes and decorations, especially those worn or carried in formal ceremonies.
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;​Example: The queen&amp;#39;s regalia at her coronation included her crown and sceptre.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
