	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;meltdown&amp;quot; &lt;/strong&gt;is the most appropriate choice to fill in the blank as it accurately describes a significant decline or collapse, &lt;strong&gt;which fits the context of market reactions.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
